    {
      "name": "Physical Attack Matrix II",
      "type": "text",
      "text": {
        "format": 1,
        "content": "<p>Use Matrix II for creatures and natural attacks without a listed weapon class.</p><p>Cross the defender’s descending armor class with the attacker’s hit-dice bracket.</p>\n    <div style=\"overflow-x:auto;margin:0.75rem 0\">\n      <table style=\"border-collapse:collapse;width:max-content;min-width:100%;font-size:0.86rem\">\n        \n        <thead><tr><th>AC</th><th>1</th><th>2-3</th><th>4-5</th><th>6-8</th><th>9-10</th><th>11-14</th><th>15+</th></tr></thead>\n        <tbody><tr><th scope=\"row\">1</th><td>20</td><td>19</td><td>18</td><td>17</td><td>16</td><td>15</td><td>14</td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">2</th><td>19</td><td>18</td><td>17</td><td>16</td><td>15</td><td>14</td><td>13</td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">3</th><td>18</td><td>17</td><td>16</td><td>15</td><td>14</td><td>13</td><td>12</td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">4</th><td>17</td><td>16</td><td>15</td><td>14</td><td>13</td><td>12</td><td>11</td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">5</th><td>16</td><td>15</td><td>14</td><td>13</td><td>12</td><td>11</td><td>10</td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">6</th><td>14</td><td>13</td><td>12</td><td>11</td><td>10</td><td>9</td><td>8</td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">7</th><td>13</td><td>12</td><td>11</td><td>10</td><td>9</td><td>8</td><td>7</td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">8</th><td>12</td><td>11</td><td>10</td><td>9</td><td>8</td><td>7</td><td>6</td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">9</th><td>11</td><td>10</td><td>9</td><td>8</td><td>7</td><td>6</td><td>5</td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">10</th><td>10</td><td>9</td><td>8</td><td>7</td><td>6</td><td>5</td><td>4</td></tr></tbody>\n      </table>\n    </div>"
